{"tid":2051750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星金管局指香港等地資金流入當地增加","createTime":"2020-06-05T04:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T04:30:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42f5304bb52aa2264521a602d5f919a4062fdbf1","tid":2051750,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:13:27.000Z","msg":"星金管局指香港等地資金流入當地增加<br />\n05.06.2020 11:54<br />\n<br />\n新加坡央行數據顯示，4月份非國民在銀行的存款，較去年同期增長44%，達到破紀錄的621.4億新加坡元，折合443.7億美元，是連續第四個月增加。新加坡金管局表示，自去年年中以來，包括香港在內，多個司法管轄區的非國民存款流入新加坡的情況普遍增加，但受新型冠狀病毒疫情引起的市場波動影響，近幾個月來資金流量變得不穩定。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，香港去年政治動盪升級，加上中美貿易戰以及疫情爆發，增加新加坡作為避風港的吸引力，吸引資金流入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1300273&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1300273%26csid%3D261_341&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5Ep1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c64a7d49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1300273&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"cbd88ab2d29dd34d7e12b2bbcb5fd5b8520af2b8","tid":2051750,"uid":5789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"波叔又話冇流出嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a939b0bd33b320dc4246dad98673a4d8e141d0","tid":2051750,"uid":106321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbd88ab2d29dd34d7e12b2bbcb5fd5b8520af2b8","tid":2051750,"uid":5789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"波叔又話冇流出嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"波叔：我就嚟襟唔住個大話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801023728a4e06af0d8b4e8295e70a3e6211507f","tid":2051750,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbd88ab2d29dd34d7e12b2bbcb5fd5b8520af2b8","tid":2051750,"uid":5789,